quotes.quote: I'm not superstitious, but I'm a little stitious.

quotes.quote: Operator! Give me the number for 911!

quotes.quote: I've always liked the notion of meeting the great figures of history. But then I think, what if it's like high school and all the really cool dead people don't want to hang out with me? Mozart will tell me he's busy but then later I'll see him out with Shakespeare and Lincoln!

quotes.quote: Interesting. You're afraid of insects and women. Ladybugs must render you catatonic.
